課程教材 Course Material
	    教科書：
1. Eugene Hecht, "Optics 4th ed.", Pearson/Addison Wesley (2002) Chapter 8~ Chapter 11
2. S.O. Kasap, "Optoelectronics and photonics : principles and practices, 2nd ed.", Pearson (2013), Chapter 1~Chapter 2

Hecht, "Optics, 4th ed.", Chapter 8 Polarization 
Hecht, "Optics, 4th ed.", Chapter 9 Interference 
第一次期中考
Hecht, "Optics, 4th ed.", Chapter 10 Diffraction
Hecht, "Optics, 4th ed.", Chapter 11 Fourier Optics
Hecht, "Optics, 4th ed.", Chapter 12 Basics of Coherence Theory
第二次期中考
Kasap, "Optoelectronics and photonics : principles and practices, 2nd ed.", Chapter 1 Wave Nature of Light
Kasap, "Optoelectronics and photonics : principles and practices, 2nd ed.", Chapter 2 Dielectric Waveguidudes and Optics Fibers
期末考     

參考書目 References
	    1. Bahaa E.A. Saleh,and Malvin Carl Teich, "Fundamentals of photonics, 2nd ed.", Wiley Interscience (2007)    

備註 Remarks





基本素養 Basic Literacy
□ 具備專業倫理、社會責任、人文涵養與國際視野
 possession of professional ethics, social responsibility, humanity and culture , and global vision
 

核心能力 Competence
■ 具備基礎科學(數學、物理、化學)與光電工程的知識
 possession of knowledge in fundamental science (mathematics, physics, chemistry) and photonics
■ 辨識與規劃解決光電工程問題的能力
 capability to identify and solve photonic problems and issues
□ 設計與執行光電實驗與工程實務的能力
 capability to design and conduct photonic experiments and engineering practices
■ 分析與解釋光電相關現象與效應的能力
 capability to analyze and explain photonic phenomena and effects
■ 整合光電、物理、化學、材料與電機等跨領域的能力
 capability for interdisciplinary integration among photonics, physics, chemistry, materials, and electrical engineering
□ 具備有效的溝通能力，以及團隊合作的精神
 capability for effective communication and team work
■ 掌握科學與社會發展，並擁有獨自與持續學習的能力
 capability to catch up with science and social developments, and to learn independently and continuously
□ 增強外文能力
 improvement in foreign languages
 

課程概述 Course Description
       本課程為光電系大三學生共同必修，在建立學生對於光電科學各方面的基礎知識，以協助學生進入專業課程的研讀與研究工作。 

課程學習目標 Course Objectives    
	    光電子學導論(一)(二)為光學(一)(二)的延伸進階課程，內容包含，光學現象(偏振，干涉，繞射)，雷射(光與原子作用，雷射光束，雷射發光機制等等)，光波導(光波導原理，光纖原理)，半導體光電(半導體發光原理，半導體雷射，發光二極體)。    

課程進度 Course Outline


週次 Week進度說明 Progress Description
1Introduction to this course and Interference (1)2Interference (2)3Interference (3)4Diffraction (1)5Diffraction (2)6第一次期中考 + Fourier Optics (1)7Fourier Optics (2)8Fourier Optics (3)9Basics of Coherence Theory (1)10Basics of Coherence Theory (2)11Basics of Coherence Theory (3)12第二次期中考 + Wave Nature of Light (1)13Wave Nature of Light (2)14Wave Nature of Light (3)15Dielectric Waveguides and Optics Fibers (1)16Dielectric Waveguides and Optics Fibers (2)17Dielectric Waveguides and Optics Fibers (3)18期末考 

　以上每週進度教師可依上課情況做適度調整。The schedule may be subject to change.


